snippet.title: Asphalt 3 Street Rules Demo Gameplay (N-Gage 2.0)
snippet.description:
Asphalt 3 Street Rules Demo, preloaded on N-Gage 2.0, Nokia N95 (N95-1 / RM-159) with Symbian OS 9.2, 332 MHz Dual ARM 11 CPU, 3D Graphics HW Accelerator (OpenGL ES 1.1, HW accelerated Java 3D) and 64 MB RAM. Game footage recorded using N95's TV-Out feature.

Check out more awesome N-Gage 2.0 games : https://goo.gl/6fLdQK
